{"tid":489330,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"新電腦用左唔夠半年 要開到機同中六合彩無分別","createTime":"2017-12-04T14:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T02:10:39.000Z","uid":38470,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"acf0cbd0adc2884d2e9ab84bbae98b93ebb34b9f","tid":489330,"uid":38470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:43:28.000Z","msg":"早兩個月 我老母同我講話部機開唔到<br />\n咁我放工即刻翻到屋企睇下發生咩事<br />\n一翻到去開機 主機板無紅燈 但係見到箱入面係有燈<br />\n咁我就boot機再開 又開到機喎 用住打機都無事<br />\n我就以為無乜野就無理部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過左一星期 部機又黎料 又係無紅燈但係箱入面有燈<br />\n拎左去電腦鋪整 個電腦友測完之後話 有好多零件壞左都有呢個情況 有機會係壞主機板、壞ram、壞顯卡.... 佢叫我拎啲零件去代理度問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後幾個星期我拎左主機板、顯卡、ram去唔同代理問 個個都話無事 試既時候又係開到機 翻到去用到一兩日之後又打柴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我真係寧願舊零件壞撚哂 都好過而家 唔知邊度壞 唔係無錢買塊新板、新顯卡 係怕買完之後原來唔係壞呢件<br />\n<br />\n呢排一星期先開到一次機 唔想再逐個零件拎去代理整 部機係centralfield俾錢砌既 拎去整又話一個月 我又怕俾人換零件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以求師兄們幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 指教小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0b14b3cbea6688898c7ae0d1cf97b69e387e67","tid":489330,"uid":3122,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"新顯卡"},{"pid":"4a42b64b8d49528cbd7ada7c323300ed408a1ac5","tid":489330,"uid":97451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:45:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e95c2b121b68035514ea2c49c38414a091a1088","tid":489330,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:45:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f88d0e501632f271653e2bd1f7edc770b10c993","tid":489330,"uid":38470,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自已砌定搵人砌？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入centralfield搵個sales 俾個budget佢幫我佩零件"},{"pid":"9c9846d25a045a3d61a39f06b66558b4420cbb63","tid":489330,"uid":74207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:47:41.000Z","msg":"我唔信我唔信，我覺得中六合彩難啲"},{"pid":"fcfbf800970bb22c9ab38e42df9f7ba3e7fa7cb2","tid":489330,"uid":38470,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:48:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新顯卡</blockquote><br />\n我怕買完唔係壞顯卡 又掉成千銀"},{"pid":"8eafc72f7890896529f78212ffe9875b8bcbca3c","tid":489330,"uid":38470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>衰火牛？</blockquote><br />\n暫時無測試過火牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f30a1d7aebc083def5f1b3eb20eb7d17189bfa","tid":489330,"uid":88029,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:49:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c049443786792313c60da00f4daf4362a7ed16da","tid":489330,"uid":64290,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:51:00.000Z","msg":"會唔會係線路接觸不良"},{"pid":"53c2e25d7686e07dcf805e0f5d0ddad3870e082e","tid":489330,"uid":74846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:51:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該壞火牛，<span style=\"color: red;\">上淘寶買料</span>，自己砌機啦！唔好再比香港啲傻尻厄，開電腦鋪班人都無料既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c67379ad87865890ccff5a6c0fa030c3bd903c","tid":489330,"uid":50458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:53:01.000Z","msg":"比個list睇睇"},{"pid":"30ecb1014c8497dfd5ee196e2b69b42ed095815d","tid":489330,"uid":38470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該壞火牛，上淘寶買料，自己砌機啦！唔好再比香港啲傻尻厄，開電腦鋪班人都無料既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我呢度間電腦鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  收我兩舊水連原因都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8007d2966786c5ceb3f4d9bb7efb58b8977e9a9","tid":489330,"uid":38470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:54:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係線路接觸不良</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以點check?"},{"pid":"fa90dfb657802bbf139bc327410ba43a3d898fe3","tid":489330,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:54:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9727ab15a23df600a430a6a897044c13ba3a7c50","tid":489330,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:55:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該壞火牛，上淘寶買料，自己砌機啦！唔好再比香港啲傻尻厄，開電腦鋪班人都無料既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我呢度間電腦鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  收我兩舊水連原因都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最怕佢換左你野你唔知<br />\n我試過佢拎左走我張顯示卡<br />\n追返佢話自己唔記得插<br />\n好彩check左<br />\n痴9 線"},{"pid":"3350edefa2bec52911b39cd880e53a94052a774b","tid":489330,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:56:11.000Z","msg":"似火牛<br />\n你比條list出黎睇下先啦 就咁問上帝都答你唔到啦"},{"pid":"cc88dfb8bfc3a9f44300e02887579b74576e3cc6","tid":489330,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會唔會係線路接觸不良</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以點check?</blockquote><br />\n由簡單開始<br />\n所有一插頭果d重新插一次<br />\n話唔定鬆左或者太污糟<br />\n仲係有事就由火牛check起"},{"pid":"f197446be2514e4e0a749d13d6f04464f977a51b","tid":489330,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"等睇你地比人咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28172a925aeebc626eac2157bc066ca88450e93e","tid":489330,"uid":81703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:56:45.000Z","msg":"死老鼠"},{"pid":"2a53281c8da4b60d28d58a493569cdd3ef764edb","tid":489330,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:56:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f55e76e8a8f3a612a8f6b345e13828f48a063808","tid":489330,"uid":38470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:57:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比個list睇睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會搵到咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82d3f4de55022ee8e7f76929799ef631118c251","tid":489330,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比個list睇睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會搵到咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇你係咪跑車牛綠色碟個d仇人list"},{"pid":"1f9acbf9e725c317db80d90d6e70e2f9437aad46","tid":489330,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>比個list睇睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會搵到咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇你係咪跑車牛綠色碟個d仇人list</blockquote><br />\n仇人機用到半年?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84830f4df25d5521874f7f8dee8d84acf44b6c47","tid":489330,"uid":156135,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:00:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比個list睇睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會搵到咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁咪知你隻牛推唔推得哂d 野囉，比你就比啦"},{"pid":"c35e55982664299233334b309a2de5cf41a3e2f3","tid":489330,"uid":38470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:01:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>衰火牛？</blockquote><br />\n暫時無測試過火牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n通常壞ram 同顯卡，都會bb聲！ <br />\n<br />\n壞底板就唔著機！ <br />\n<br />\n開唔到機，自動關機就壞火牛, 或者cpu 個冷風機，或者散熱膏唔夠！！ <br />\n<br />\n硬碟機壞就入唔到windows !<br />\n<br />\n電腦鋪話你壞ram 壞顯卡，就知佢無料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一開始都諗住壞板 點知去到代理又開到 試過開四五次都無問題 如果平時我開到機 用幾耐都唔會自動關機 粒u我都check過 佢都話無事 仲同我茶左新散熱膏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b404c370cd7e7b7717f39e0853f6b24f27b93926","tid":489330,"uid":38470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/231040_9c921f42a66959e3d6df813ad21f2ad5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F231040_9c921f42a66959e3d6df813ad21f2ad5.jpg&h=c029663a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b4f664938a86023beda9c49e8636e08bc54c05d","tid":489330,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:13:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43a2153ac4694bce5964ec5be88612ce6116d0d8","tid":489330,"uid":38470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:15:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/231040_9c921f42a66959e3d6df813ad21f2ad5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F231040_9c921f42a66959e3d6df813ad21f2ad5.jpg&h=c029663a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢部咁既野，你砌左幾錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />